  "body": "### Description\r\nOur EL client fell behind and Teku stopped performing its duties but /readiness endpoint still returned 200 OK. Some errors seen in teku:\r\n\r\n```\r\n | 2022-09-21 09:29:03 | Caused by: java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: Cannot get active validator indices from an epoch beyond the seed lookahead period. Requested epoch 148241 from state in epoch 14823\r\n...\r\n | 2022-09-21 09:29:04 | java.util.concurrent.CompletionException: java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: Invalid remote response: Failed to connect to execution-client-teku-beacon-2/10.0.125.57:8550\r\n...\r\n| 2022-09-21 09:29:04 | 2022-09-21 08:29:04.053 ERROR - Failed to update fork choice\r\n...\r\n```\r\nAnd teku was not following the chain in that period.\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce (Bug)\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior:** /readiness endpoint should return a 50x error code\r\n\r\n**Actual behavior:** /readiness endpoint returns 200 OK\r\n\r\n### Versions (Add all that apply)\r\n* Software version: 22.9.1",
